{"word":"παραπορεύομαι","slug":"παραπορεύομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παραπορεύομαι</b></el> <p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>, with <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>mid.</a> and aor1 <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a>,<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to go beside</i> or <i>alongside</i>, <b><a href='S:Polybius'>Polyb.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to go past</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> loci, <b><a href='S:Polybius'>Polyb.</a></b>: <i>to pass</i>, <el>διὰ τῶν σπορίμων</el> <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}